            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "**Swift Radio** is a fully featured, open-source radio station app written entirely in **Swift**. It provides robust, professional functionality out of the box, complete with **Apple CarPlay** support, making it the perfect foundation for **building** or **customizing** your own streaming radio experience."
